Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Ya, Tuhan♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Terimalah pendustaan♫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:05:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Impian yang abadi kian lenyap♫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Tak pernah sempurna, menjijikkan♫
